Module chav1961.purelib
Package chav1961.purelib.i18n.interfaces

Annotation Type LocaleResource

@Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target({FIELD,TYPE})
public @interface LocaleResource

This annotation describes any locale-specific resources associated with the given field. Field can be either JComponent instance or any class implemented LocaleSpecificTextSetter interface

Since:
0.0.2
Author:
Alexander Chernomyrdin aka chav1961
See Also:
Localizer, LocaleSpecificTextSetter

  • Element Details

    • value

      java.lang.String value

      Content value key associated with the given entity

      Returns:

      Help key associated with the given entity

      Default:
      ""

    • icon

      java.lang.String icon

      Icon associated with the given entity

      Returns:
      associated icon or null
      Default:
      ""
